\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 4. Write a query toget count of jobs failed in the last 24 hours**
\par \tab \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 SELECT COUNT(*) AS FailedJobCount
\par \tab \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 FROM JobHistory
